00:04:44.890 --> 00:04:47.223
The interesting part is that
most of the cartoons adults

00:04:47.223 --> 00:04:48.460
watch are made for adults.

00:04:48.460 --> 00:04:50.960
"The Simpsons," "Bob's Burgers,"
"Family Guy," "South Park,"

00:04:50.960 --> 00:04:54.460
